{"tid":1602662,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"翻唔到轉頭","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T21:24:31.000Z","uid":218219,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"486e5dcc56a2fe5c678947bca8071372bfb02abb","tid":1602662,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"香港翻唔到轉頭<br />\n自己都翻唔到轉頭<br />\n已經冇辦法去翻以前個心態咁 正常地搵工讀書寫故<br />\n無論做咗幾多嘢麻醉自己都冇效<br />\n就算去睇醫生 醫生都唔會幫到我 佢唔會改變到我人生同香港<br />\n唔想連累所有認識嘅人 唔想成為包袱<br />\n我聽講過 如果再冇人記得某個人 咁佢就同死咗冇分別<br />\n我諗我已經成功咗一大半"},{"pid":"322727b7e52a50f81578211a914d9470f7ba6f1a","tid":1602662,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"認同，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e975ac511782d921e374f35822ca043abd60a4","tid":1602662,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a754e4b7c1c8a5803fb131d490ad80ac7bb9071a","tid":1602662,"uid":247522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:08:22.000Z","msg":"唔需要返轉頭....每段經歷都係成長既一部份<br />\n有痛苦 有悲傷 但總會有快樂既時候<br />\n<br />\n如果現實同香港都令你感覺唔到愛<br />\n<br />\n多上連登 連登有愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeec286479b095fa583c384b6d6148fa8f8b437a","tid":1602662,"uid":156751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"小野菊姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油啊<br />\n我會支持你㗎"},{"pid":"64db62806d89dac004892764c7c9740184af9673","tid":1602662,"uid":1419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"加油啊樓主，上連登大把巴絲會撐住你㗎"},{"pid":"3c06a90ad8900c310674d4174136ca661853e9be","tid":1602662,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64db62806d89dac004892764c7c9740184af9673","tid":1602662,"uid":1419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T